warnings: For external use only. Flammable. Keep away from fire or flame. Stop using and ask medical attention if redness and irritation develop and persist for more than 72 hours. Do not store above 40 Celsius Degree (105 Fahrenheit). Do not use in mouth, ears or eyes. In case of contact, flush eyes with water.
dosage_administration: Pump as needed into your palms and thoroughly spread on both hands, and rub the skin until dry. Children must be supervised in use of this product.
indications: keep out of eyes when water, soap and towel are not available
